column5: DAYUM!!!! Them Ausies will take their trucks through anything.
No thanx!  I have a boat for travelling the H2O highway.
Must be nice to have money
I used to watch the Aussie fishing shows years back; Rex Hunt, Steve and Bushy. They drive through anything, and offroad is how you get to a fishing hole.
I have been through some deep water on the trails but that is crazy ! Keep your foot down and don't let off her
